data.description: This home is priced to move!! 3bd/2ba 1347sqft home with 2 car detached garage and ample amount of storage rooms for all your toys. Priceless views of the lake, sandy beach, new deck and concrete driveway for easy access. Nice grandfathered dock and outdoor fitpit. Private septic and well producing well. 95'ft of frontage. One of the lower lease fees at $15,200/year for 2014. Great investment lot!
